metrics.visualTitle: Sum of Forecast by Day and Model

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"ARIMA"}, 'ForecastResults'[Model])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'LocalDateTable_f4286e06-ecf3-4163-8bbc-ab0edfddd3e2'[Day],
			'ForecastResults'[Model],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			"SumForecast", CALCULATE(SUM('ForecastResults'[Forecast]))
		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0PrimaryDbCount = 
		CALCULATE(
			COUNTROWS(
				SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'LocalDateTable_f4286e06-ecf3-4163-8bbc-ab0edfddd3e2'[Day])
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryDbCount = 
		CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'ForecastResults'[Model])))

	VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
		SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(
			3500,
			__DS0Core,
			'LocalDateTable_f4286e06-ecf3-4163-8bbc-ab0edfddd3e2'[Day],
			[SumForecast],
			350,
			'ForecastResults'[Model],
			ALPHABETICAL,
			ASC,
			105000,
			60
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0BodyBinnedSample, 'ForecastResults'[Model])

	VAR __DS0SecondaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0SecondaryBase))

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
			__DS0BodyBinnedSample,
			"ColumnIndex",
			__DS0SecondaryBase,
			'ForecastResults'[Model],
			ASC
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount,
		"DS0PrimaryDbCount", __DS0PrimaryDbCount,
		"DS0SecondaryDbCount", __DS0SecondaryDbCount,
		"DS0SecondaryCount", __DS0SecondaryCount
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0SecondaryBase

ORDER BY
	'ForecastResults'[Model]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'LocalDateTable_f4286e06-ecf3-4163-8bbc-ab0edfddd3e2'[Day], [ColumnIndex]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"ARIMA"}, 'ForecastResults'[Model])

	VAR __DS0Core =

metrics.visualTitle: Forecast by Month, Day and Model

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"ARIMA"}, 'ForecastResults'[Model])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'LocalDateTable_b942e7f7-2004-4b07-b5e4-52cae8bc461d'[Day],

			'LocalDateTable_b942e7f7-2004-4b07-b5e4-52cae8bc461d'[MonthNo],
			'Arima vs Lstm'[Model],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			"SumForecast", CALCULATE(SUM('Arima vs Lstm'[Forecast]))
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(
			201,
			SUMMARIZE(
				__DS0Core,
				'LocalDateTable_b942e7f7-2004-4b07-b5e4-52cae8bc461d'[Day],
				'LocalDateTable_b942e7f7-2004-4b07-b5e4-52cae8bc461d'[Month],
				'LocalDateTable_b942e7f7-2004-4b07-b5e4-52cae8bc461d'[MonthNo]
			),
			'LocalDateTable_b942e7f7-2004-4b07-b5e4-52cae8bc461d'[MonthNo],
			1,
			'LocalDateTable_b942e7f7-2004-4b07-b5e4-52cae8bc461d'[Month],
			1,
			'LocalDateTable_b942e7f7-2004-4b07-b5e4-52cae8bc461d'[Day],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Arima vs Lstm'[Model])

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(62, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'Arima vs Lstm'[Model], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryWindowed,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0Core,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'Arima vs Lstm'[Model],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'Arima vs Lstm'[Model]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'LocalDateTable_b942e7f7-2004-4b07-b5e4-52cae8bc461d'[MonthNo],
	'LocalDateTable_b942e7f7-2004-4b07-b5e4-52cae8bc461d'[Month],
	'LocalDateTable_b942e7f7-2004-4b07-b5e4-52cae8bc461d'[Day],
	[ColumnIndex]

DEFINE
	VAR __H0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"ARIMA"}, 'ForecastResults'[Model])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'LocalDateTable_e6e1dfd3-7493-45d8-92e8-9826d47e4462'[Day],
			'LSTM vs HWES'[Model],
			"SumForecast", CALCULATE(SUM('LSTM vs HWES'[Forecast])),
			"LSTM_vs_HWESSumForecast", IGNORE(
				CALCULATE(SUM('LSTM vs HWES'[Forecast]), KEEPFILTERS(__H0FilterTable))
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'LocalDateTable_e6e1dfd3-7493-45d8-92e8-9826d47e4462'[Day])

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'LSTM vs HWES'[Model])

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0PrimaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0PrimaryBase))

	VAR __DS0SecondaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0SecondaryBase))

	VAR __DS0SpaceCount = (__DS0PrimaryCount * __DS0SecondaryCount)

	VAR __DS0SparseFactor = MIN(5, DIVIDE(__DS0SpaceCount, __DS0IntersectionCount))

	VAR __DS0TargetIntersectionCount = CEILING(3500 * __DS0SparseFactor, 1)

	VAR __DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0IntersectionCount <= 3500,
			IF(
				__DS0SpaceCount <= __DS0TargetIntersectionCount,
				3500,
				FLOOR(
					SQRT(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount * DIVIDE(__DS0PrimaryCount, __DS0SecondaryCount)),
					1
				)
			),
			IF(
				AND(__DS0PrimaryCount > 800, __DS0SecondaryCount > 60),
				CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, 60), 1),
				IF(
					__DS0SecondaryCount > 60,
					__DS0PrimaryCount,
					CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0SecondaryCount), 1)
				)
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0IntersectionCount <= 3500,
			IF(
				__DS0SpaceCount <= __DS0TargetIntersectionCount,
				3500,
				FLOOR(
					DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, FLOOR(
						SQRT(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount * DIVIDE(__DS0PrimaryCount, __DS0SecondaryCount)),
						1
					)),
					1
				)
			),
			IF(
				AND(__DS0PrimaryCount > 800, __DS0SecondaryCount > 60),
				60,
				IF(
					__DS0SecondaryCount > 60,
					CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0PrimaryCount), 1),
					__DS0SecondaryCount
				)
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0MinPrimaryCount = MIN(10, __DS0PrimaryCount)

	VAR __DS0MinSecondaryCount = MIN(10, __DS0SecondaryCount)

	VAR __DS0TargetPrimaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount < __DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			__DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			IF(
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount < __DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0MinSecondaryCount), 1),
				__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0TargetSecondaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount < __DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0MinPrimaryCount), 1),
			IF(
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount < __DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				__DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0Primary = 
		SAMPLE(
			__DS0TargetPrimaryCount + 2,
			__DS0PrimaryBase,
			'LocalDateTable_e6e1dfd3-7493-45d8-92e8-9826d47e4462'[Day],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(__DS0TargetSecondaryCount + 1, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'LSTM vs HWES'[Model], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyWithLimitedSecondary = 
		NATURALINNERJOIN(
			__DS0Core,
			__DS0Secondary
		)

	VAR __DS0KeyValues = 
		GROUPBY(
			__DS0BodyWithLimitedSecondary,
			'LSTM vs HWES'[Model],
			"MinSumForecast", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [SumForecast]),
			"MaxSumForecast", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), [SumForecast])
		)

	VAR __DS0KeyPoints = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(
				FILTER(
					KEEPFILTERS(NATURALINNERJOIN(
						__DS0BodyWithLimitedSecondary,
						__DS0KeyValues
					)),
					AND(
						AND(
							OR([SumForecast] = [MinSumForecast], [SumForecast] = [MaxSumForecast]),
							NOT([MinSumForecast] = [MaxSumForecast])
						),
						NOT([SumForecast] = 0)
					)
				)
			),
			"'LocalDateTable_e6e1dfd3-7493-45d8-92e8-9826d47e4462'[Day]", 'LocalDateTable_e6e1dfd3-7493-45d8-92e8-9826d47e4462'[Day],
			"'LSTM vs HWES'[Model]", 'LSTM vs HWES'[Model],
			"SumForecast", [SumForecast],
			"LSTM_vs_HWESSumForecast", [LSTM_vs_HWESSumForecast]
		)

	VAR __DS0KeyPrimaryLimit = CEILING(DIVIDE(350, __DS0TargetSecondaryCount), 1)

	VAR __DS0KeyPrimaryValuesLimited = 
		TOPN(
			__DS0KeyPrimaryLimit,
			SUMMARIZE(__DS0KeyPoints, 'LocalDateTable_e6e1dfd3-7493-45d8-92e8-9826d47e4462'[Day]),
			'LocalDateTable_e6e1dfd3-7493-45d8-92e8-9826d47e4462'[Day],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0KeyPrimaryLimitedCount = 
		CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0KeyPrimaryValuesLimited))

	VAR __DS0PrimaryKeyPoints = 
		DISTINCT(UNION(__DS0Primary, __DS0KeyPrimaryValuesLimited))

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryKeyPoints,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0BodyWithLimitedSecondary,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'LSTM vs HWES'[Model],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount,
		"DS0PrimaryCount", __DS0PrimaryCount,
		"DS0TargetPrimaryCount", __DS0TargetPrimaryCount,
		"DS0SecondaryCount", __DS0SecondaryCount,
		"DS0TargetSecondaryCount", __DS0TargetSecondaryCount,
		"DS0KeyPrimaryLimitedCount", __DS0KeyPrimaryLimitedCount,
		"DS0KeyPrimaryLimit", __DS0KeyPrimaryLimit
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'LSTM vs HWES'[Model]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'LocalDateTable_e6e1dfd3-7493-45d8-92e8-9826d47e4462'[Day], [ColumnIndex]

			),

	VAR __DS0PrimaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'LocalDateTable_e6e1dfd3-7493-45d8-92e8-9826d47e4462'[Day])

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'LSTM vs HWES'[Model])

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0PrimaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0PrimaryBase))

	VAR __DS0SecondaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0SecondaryBase))

	VAR __DS0SpaceCount = (__DS0PrimaryCount * __DS0SecondaryCount)

	VAR __DS0SparseFactor = MIN(5, DIVIDE(__DS0SpaceCount, __DS0IntersectionCount))

	VAR __DS0TargetIntersectionCount = CEILING(3500 * __DS0SparseFactor, 1)

	VAR __DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0IntersectionCount <= 3500,
			IF(
				__DS0SpaceCount <= __DS0TargetIntersectionCount,
				3500,
				FLOOR(
					SQRT(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount * DIVIDE(__DS0PrimaryCount, __DS0SecondaryCount)),
					1
				)
			),
			IF(
				AND(__DS0PrimaryCount > 800, __DS0SecondaryCount > 60),
				CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, 60), 1),
				IF(
					__DS0SecondaryCount > 60,
					__DS0PrimaryCount,
					CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0SecondaryCount), 1)
				)
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0IntersectionCount <= 3500,
			IF(
				__DS0SpaceCount <= __DS0TargetIntersectionCount,
				3500,
				FLOOR(
					DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, FLOOR(
						SQRT(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount * DIVIDE(__DS0PrimaryCount, __DS0SecondaryCount)),
						1
					)),
					1
				)
			),
			IF(
				AND(__DS0PrimaryCount > 800, __DS0SecondaryCount > 60),
				60,
				IF(
					__DS0SecondaryCount > 60,
					CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0PrimaryCount), 1),
					__DS0SecondaryCount
				)
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0MinPrimaryCount = MIN(10, __DS0PrimaryCount)

	VAR __DS0MinSecondaryCount = MIN(10, __DS0SecondaryCount)

	VAR __DS0TargetPrimaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount < __DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			__DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			IF(
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount < __DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0MinSecondaryCount), 1),
				__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0TargetSecondaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount < __DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0MinPrimaryCount), 1),
			IF(
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount < __DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				__DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0Primary =

		)

		)

						__DS0KeyValues
					)),
					AND(
						AND(
							OR([SumForecast] = [MinSumForecast], [SumForecast] = [MaxSumForecast]),
							NOT([MinSumForecast] = [MaxSumForecast])
						),
						NOT([SumForecast] = 0)
					)
				)
			),
			"'LocalDateTable_e6e1dfd3-7493-45d8-92e8-9826d47e4462'[Day]", 'LocalDateTable_e6e1dfd3-7493-45d8-92e8-9826d47e4462'[Day],

		)

	VAR __DS0TargetSecondaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount < __DS0MinPrimaryCount,
			CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, __DS0MinPrimaryCount), 1),
			IF(
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount < __DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				__DS0MinSecondaryCount,
				__DS0InitTargetSecondaryCount
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0Primary = 
		SAMPLE(
			__DS0TargetPrimaryCount + 2,
			__DS0PrimaryBase,
			'LocalDateTable_8f93cd67-06a4-4f91-8535-d737489039b6'[Day],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(__DS0TargetSecondaryCount + 1, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'Lstm vs Prophet'[Model], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyWithLimitedSecondary = 
		NATURALINNERJOIN(
			__DS0Core,
			__DS0Secondary
		)

	VAR __DS0KeyValues = 
		GROUPBY(
			__DS0BodyWithLimitedSecondary,
			'Lstm vs Prophet'[Model],
			"MinSumForecast", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [SumForecast]),
			"MaxSumForecast", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), [SumForecast])
		)

	VAR __DS0KeyPoints = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(
				FILTER(
					KEEPFILTERS(NATURALINNERJOIN(
						__DS0BodyWithLimitedSecondary,
						__DS0KeyValues
					)),
					AND(
						AND(
							OR([SumForecast] = [MinSumForecast], [SumForecast] = [MaxSumForecast]),
							NOT([MinSumForecast] = [MaxSumForecast])
						),
						NOT([SumForecast] = 0)
					)
				)
			),
			"'LocalDateTable_8f93cd67-06a4-4f91-8535-d737489039b6'[Day]", 'LocalDateTable_8f93cd67-06a4-4f91-8535-d737489039b6'[Day],
			"'Lstm vs Prophet'[Model]", 'Lstm vs Prophet'[Model],
			"SumForecast", [SumForecast]
		)

	VAR __DS0KeyPrimaryLimit = CEILING(DIVIDE(350, __DS0TargetSecondaryCount), 1)

	VAR __DS0KeyPrimaryValuesLimited = 
		TOPN(
			__DS0KeyPrimaryLimit,
			SUMMARIZE(__DS0KeyPoints, 'LocalDateTable_8f93cd67-06a4-4f91-8535-d737489039b6'[Day]),
			'LocalDateTable_8f93cd67-06a4-4f91-8535-d737489039b6'[Day],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0KeyPrimaryLimitedCount = 
		CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0KeyPrimaryValuesLimited))

	VAR __DS0PrimaryKeyPoints = 
		DISTINCT(UNION(__DS0Primary, __DS0KeyPrimaryValuesLimited))

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryKeyPoints,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0BodyWithLimitedSecondary,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'Lstm vs Prophet'[Model],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount,
		"DS0PrimaryCount", __DS0PrimaryCount,
		"DS0TargetPrimaryCount", __DS0TargetPrimaryCount,
		"DS0SecondaryCount", __DS0SecondaryCount,
		"DS0TargetSecondaryCount", __DS0TargetSecondaryCount,
		"DS0KeyPrimaryLimitedCount", __DS0KeyPrimaryLimitedCount,
		"DS0KeyPrimaryLimit", __DS0KeyPrimaryLimit
	)

EVALUATE
